Kubernetes Autoscaling
======================
1.Horizontal pod autoscaler(HPA)
2.Vertical pod autoscaler(VPA)
3.Cluster Autoscaler(CA)

1.In vertical pod autoscaler we increase the resources of existing pods.
2.Horizontal pod auto scaler scales based on resource metric of pods.

How HPA works?
===============


Controller                           Worker
                                     metric
Metric Server <-------------kubelet <--------Pods(C Adviser agent)
    |
Api server
    |
HPA controller

